      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, an exemplar of automotive excellence that remains in showroom condition. This specimen has been curated with fastidious attention to detail, showing no signs of wear and retaining its original luster and mechanical precision. Every surface, from the hand-finished interior to the flawless exterior paintwork, reflects a standard of care that is rarely encountered in the secondary market. For the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing short of perfection, this vehicle represents a premier investment in both performance and prestige.",
      "price": 48500.0,
